32. Musician Noel Gallagher of Oasis is 32. Musician Chan Kinchla 
of Blues Traveler is 30. Singer Melanie Brown (Mel B.-Scary Spice) 
of Spice Girls is 24. Rapper Playa Poncho is 24. 
</P>
