<HEADLINE> London Shares Close Higher / British Stocks  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	LONDON (AP) -- Share prices rose Wednesday on the London Stock  
Exchange. 
</P>
<P>
	The Financial Times-Stock Exchange 100-share index rose 60.30  
points, or 1.0 percent, to 6,266.70. 
</P>
<P>
	Provisional volume was 1 billion shares compared with 950  
million shares on Tuesday. 
