<CATEGORY> sports </CATEGORY>
<HEADLINE>  Sabres, Leafs: Great Lakes Showdown / Hockey Game Story  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	TORONTO (AP) -- Many Toronto sports fans have a soft spot for  
Buffalo, a small-market city with Canadian-style winters, just 100 
miles away. 
</P>
<P>
	Temporarily, though, the Peace Bridge that links Buffalo to  
